---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Cancellation and Refunds - tech-lessons.in">
    <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto font-sans">
        <section class="mb-12">
            <h1 class="font-sans font-bold text-3xl mb-4 text-zinc-900">
                Cancellation and Refunds
            </h1>
            <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm font-sans mt-1">
                Last updated: July 2026
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-8">
            <p class="text-zinc-600 text-base leading-relaxed font-sans">
                Because our technical trainings have strictly capped seating to
                maintain a highly interactive, small-group engineering
                environment, we operate under a transparent refund framework:
            </p>

            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="font-sans font-bold text-lg text-zinc-900 mb-2">
                        Pre-Training Cancellations
                    </h3>
                    <p
                        class="text-zinc-600 text-base leading-relaxed font-sans"
                    >
                        If you need to cancel your registration, you can request
                        a full 100% refund up to 7 days before the live training
                        officially begins.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h3 class="font-sans font-bold text-lg text-zinc-900 mb-2">
                        First-Weekend Guarantee
                    </h3>
                    <p
                        class="text-zinc-600 text-base leading-relaxed font-sans"
                    >
                        We offer a first-weekend money-back guarantee. If you
                        decide the course is not a good fit for you after
                        completing the first weekend, request a refund within 48
                        hours of starting the training, and we will process a
                        100% refund. No refunds or cancellations will be
                        processed after this 48-hour window has elapsed.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h3 class="font-sans font-bold text-lg text-zinc-900 mb-2">
                        How to Request
                    </h3>
                    <p
                        class="text-zinc-600 text-base leading-relaxed font-sans"
                    >
                        To initiate a refund within the eligible window, please
                        send an email to <a
                            href="mailto:sarthak.makhija@tech-lessons.in"
                            class="text-blue-600 hover:underline font-sans"
                            >sarthak.makhija@tech-lessons.in</a
                        > with your registration details. Eligible refunds are processed
                        back to the original payment method via Razorpay within 5-7
                        working days.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</Layout>
